<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF8"?>
<document>
  <properties>
    <title>maven-flex-plugin - flex:runtime</title>
  </properties>
  <body>
    <section name="flex:runtime">
      <p><strong>Full name</strong>:</p>
      <p>com.site.maven.plugins:maven-flex-plugin:1.0.0:runtime</p>
      <p><strong>Description</strong>:</p>
      <p>Build Flex runtime environment for a web application. Following
steps will be taken: 

<ul>
<li>Unzip Flex runtime</li>

<li>For each swf dependency in the dependencies, generate html file
from the template file and copy it to war source directory as well
as swf file</li>

<li>Copy resource files if specified</li>
</ul></p>
      <p><strong>Attributes</strong>:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Requires a Maven 2.0 project to be executed.</li>
      </ul>
      <subsection name="Required Parameters">
        <table border="0" align="left">
          <tr>
            <th>Name</th>
            <th>Type</th>
            <th>Since</th>
            <th>Description</th>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td><strong><a href="#flexRuntime">flexRuntime</a></strong></td>
            <td><code>File</code></td>
            <td><code>-</code></td>
            <td>Flex runtime zip file </td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td><strong><a href="#overwrite">overwrite</a></strong></td>
            <td><code>boolean</code></td>
            <td><code>-</code></td>
            <td>If overwrite Flex runtime files if exists Default value is: <code>false</code>.</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td><strong><a href="#template">template</a></strong></td>
            <td><code>String</code></td>
            <td><code>-</code></td>
            <td>Template file name within Flex runtime.zip. It's used as a template
to create Flex landing page for each of swf files. Default value is: <code>flex/main.html</code>.</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td><strong><a href="#warSourceDirectory">warSourceDirectory</a></strong></td>
            <td><code>String</code></td>
            <td><code>-</code></td>
            <td>war source directory of current project Default value is: <code>src/main/webapp</code>.</td>
          </tr>
        </table>
      </subsection>
      <subsection name="Optional Parameters">
        <table border="0" align="left">
          <tr>
            <th>Name</th>
            <th>Type</th>
            <th>Since</th>
            <th>Description</th>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td><strong><a href="#dependencies">dependencies</a></strong></td>
            <td><code>List</code></td>
            <td><code>-</code></td>
            <td>swf dependencies, which will be used to generate html template
files and .swf files will be copied to the war source directory </td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td><strong><a href="#resources">resources</a></strong></td>
            <td><code>List</code></td>
            <td><code>-</code></td>
            <td>Resource files need to be copied and packaged into war file.
Optional. </td>
          </tr>
        </table>
      </subsection>
      <subsection name="Parameter Details">
        <p><strong><a name="dependencies">dependencies</a>:</strong></p>
        <p>swf dependencies, which will be used to generate html template
files and .swf files will be copied to the war source directory</p>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Type</strong>: <code>java.util.List</code></li>
          <li><strong>Required</strong>: <code>No</code></li>
        </ul><hr/><p><strong><a name="flexRuntime">flexRuntime</a>:</strong></p>
        <p>Flex runtime zip file</p>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Type</strong>: <code>java.io.File</code></li>
          <li><strong>Required</strong>: <code>Yes</code></li>
        </ul><hr/><p><strong><a name="overwrite">overwrite</a>:</strong></p>
        <p>If overwrite Flex runtime files if exists</p>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Type</strong>: <code>boolean</code></li>
          <li><strong>Required</strong>: <code>Yes</code></li>
          <li><strong>Default</strong>: <code>false</code></li>
        </ul><hr/><p><strong><a name="resources">resources</a>:</strong></p>
        <p>Resource files need to be copied and packaged into war file.
Optional.</p>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Type</strong>: <code>java.util.List</code></li>
          <li><strong>Required</strong>: <code>No</code></li>
        </ul><hr/><p><strong><a name="template">template</a>:</strong></p>
        <p>Template file name within Flex runtime.zip. It's used as a template
to create Flex landing page for each of swf files.</p>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Type</strong>: <code>java.lang.String</code></li>
          <li><strong>Required</strong>: <code>Yes</code></li>
          <li><strong>Default</strong>: <code>flex/main.html</code></li>
        </ul><hr/><p><strong><a name="warSourceDirectory">warSourceDirectory</a>:</strong></p>
        <p>war source directory of current project</p>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Type</strong>: <code>java.lang.String</code></li>
          <li><strong>Required</strong>: <code>Yes</code></li>
          <li><strong>Default</strong>: <code>src/main/webapp</code></li>
        </ul>
      </subsection>
    </section>
  </body>
</document>